dc_title_s: Map of St. Marys River Basin showing availability of underground water
dc_description_s: Prepared by ALFRED C. WALKER, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water, from data compiled by Lawrence R. Brunstetter.|Scale bar lower right corner of map.|Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the St. Marys Basin, quality of underground water, and a summary.|Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
